{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id78817e81-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s705"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"705"},"text":"§ 705.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Transportation or importation of migratory birds; when unlawful","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"It shall be unlawful to ship, transport, or carry, by any means whatever, from one State, Territory, or district to or through another State, Territory, or district, or to or through a foreign country, any bird, or any part, nest, or egg thereof, captured, killed, taken, shipped, transported, or carried at any time contrary to the laws of the State, Territory, or district in which it was captured, killed, or taken, or from which it was shipped, transported, or carried. It shall be unlawful to import any bird, or any part, nest, or egg thereof, captured, killed, taken, shipped, transported, or carried contrary to the laws of any Province of the Dominion of Canada in which the same was captured, killed, or taken, or from which it was shipped, transported, or carried.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id78817e82-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1918-07-03/ch128/s4"},"text":"July 3, 1918, ch. 128, § 4","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/755"},"text":"40 Stat. 755","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1936-06-20/ch634/s4"},"text":"June 20, 1936, ch. 634, § 4","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/49/1556"},"text":"49 Stat. 1556","children":[],"tail":"; 1939 Reorg. Plan No. II, § 4(f), eff. "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1939-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1939","children":[],"tail":", 4 F.R. 2731, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/53/1433"},"text":"53 Stat. 1433","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/135/s10"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–135, § 10","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1969-12-05"},"text":"Dec. 5, 1969","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/83/282"},"text":"83 Stat. 282","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id78817e83-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id78817e84-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id78817e85-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1969—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/135"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–135","children":[],"tail":" repealed second par., which prohibited shipment of wild game mammals or parts thereof by any person of the United States to and from Mexico, except by permit from the Secretary of the Interior."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1936—Act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1936-06-20"},"text":"June 20, 1936","children":[],"tail":", inserted last sentence."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id78817e86-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id78817e87-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Ef